channel.title: mycatalog updates
channel.description: 'My Catalog' uses the IBM Cloud catalog API to retrieve data from the catalog. It attempts to be as accurate as possible. This feed shows additions, updates, removals from the catalog. Use with care. It is a work-in-progress :)

item.title: [updated] Continuous Delivery (continuous-delivery) has changed the description of the plan named professional
item.description: *before*: The Professional plan offers the full capabilities of Continuous Delivery to all users in your organization or resource group for a monthly per-user charge., *after*: The Professional plan offers the full capabilities of Continuous Delivery to all authorized users in your resource group and region for a monthly per-user charge.
